{"profile":{"awsPrograms":[{"joinedAt":2026.0,"programName":"USER_GROUP_LEADER"},{"category":"Community Hero","joinedAt":2016.0,"memberStatus":"ACTIVE","programName":"HERO"}],"basicInfo":{"alias":"shimon","avatar":"https://avatars.builderprofile.aws.dev/2hxItWI6wha9W93Ish1KdnMlicB.webp","bio":"Co-Founder and CEO of Copperhelm\n\nPreviously as the CEO and Co-Founder of Datree, a Y Combinator-backed startup, I lead a team of engineers and developers who are on a mission to prevent misconfigurations in Kubernetes, the most popular cloud-native platform. With over five years of experience in building and scaling Datree, I have developed a deep expertise in Kubernetes security, cloud-native technologies, and AWS services.\n\nI am also passionate about sharing my knowledge and insights with the global cloud community. I am a CNCF Ambassador, a co-organizer of the Israeli chapter and KCD events, and an AWS Community Hero, leading the Israeli community with 8,000 members. I co-organize UpWards PLG, a founder group for product-led growth startups. I enjoy writing and speaking about cloud-native best practices, AWS optimization, and Kubernetes challenges.","builderProfileId":"41144279-7b7f-404b-a680-d21548557576","createdOn":1.718529425408E12,"headline":"CEO & Co-Founder at Copperhelm","isStaff":false,"name":"Shimon Tolts"},"location":{"displayLocation":{"countryRegion":"IL"}},"profileStatus":"ACTIVE","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/shimont/","linkedIn":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/tolts/","youtube":"https://www.youtube.com/@ShimOnOps"}}}